Fixed. The single issue was that `MotifNode.timbral_tags` in `my-claw/tools/senseweave/score_tree.py:33` was declared as a required field with no default, but the test (and likely other call sites) constructs `MotifNode` without passing it. Changed `timbral_tags: tuple[str, ...]` to `timbral_tags: tuple[str, ...] = ()`.

